name: BladeRunner Punks
description:
The new generation of punk NFTs hit the Ethereum blockchain. 

10,000 unique dystopian NFTs with 100% CC0 to holders, newly constructed from scratch from over 100 traits to a defined BladeRunnerPunk-DNA rarity system. Forward facing and drawing eye-to-eye contact, BladeRunnerPunks emanate strong identity, status, & confidence. Inspired by the greatest sci-fi movie of all time and the greatest punk NFT collection! 

Look out for two new classes of punks: - 5 Replicants (Mythical) - 124 Androids (Legendary) 

The future is wilder than we imagine. 

Note: BladeRunnerPunks are not associated with Alcon Entertainment.
